{"tid":2092312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新疆六月飛霜 500 羊因夏天剃毛慘被凍死","createTime":"2020-07-03T07:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T11:01:06.000Z","uid":50534,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"02b885b1ca47f1aba1b023f4295269c303de7934","tid":2092312,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:07:01.000Z","msg":"近日中國水災災情嚴重，部份地方的天氣亦顯得反常。據內地媒體報道，新疆上月 29 日突然下起暴雪，氣溫隨著降低攝氏 8 至 10 度，山區氣溫最低降至零度以下，許多因夏天剃毛的羊更因此慘被凍死。<br />\n<br />\n新疆上月 29 日突然下起暴雪<br />\n山區氣溫最低降至零度以下<br />\n導致至少有 130 多輛車、400多名遊客滯留，以及近 500頭牲畜凍死<br />\n據內地媒體報道，新疆伊犁特克斯縣從 29 日起下起大雪，雪平均厚 4 厘米左右，偏遠山區積雪厚度可達 50 厘米，導致至少有 130 多輛車、400多名遊客滯留，以及近 500頭牲畜凍死。由於大雪突如其來的，不少羊由於沒有羊毛禦寒而凍死，經濟損失近百萬元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2685176/%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%85%AD%E6%9C%88%E9%A3%9B%E9%9C%9C%20500%20%E7%BE%8A%E5%9B%A0%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9%E5%89%83%E6%AF%9B%E6%85%98%E8%A2%AB%E5%87%8D%E6%AD%BB#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2685176%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E9%25A3%259B%25E9%259C%259C%2520500%2520%25E7%25BE%258A%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%25A4%258F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%2589%2583%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%2585%2598%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2587%258D%25E6%25AD%25BB%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D1&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=deedb703\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2685176/%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%85%AD%E6%9C%88%E9%A3%9B%E9%9C%9C%20500%20%E7%BE%8A%E5%9B%A0%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9%E5%89%83%E6%AF%9B%E6%85%98%E8%A2%AB%E5%87%8D%E6%AD%BB#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hV4k5h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hV4k5h.jpg&h=5700b48f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c78c8569ef3b364001f2fb66319c0c93177599f7","tid":2092312,"uid":326881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"D羊係無辜架！"},{"pid":"827f3e38587f54c135a2d2fd909f008f024f011a","tid":2092312,"uid":303830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:13:59.000Z","msg":"六月飛霜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD羊好慘"},{"pid":"40ed7032e1d2a279e16917b1e61547d416fe23a4","tid":2092312,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"新疆6月日均最低19, 最高29 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfef6824208310d14a936545e78a8a62cab80584","tid":2092312,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"即刻整羊肉祭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84c5cabd2d96babdd018c616ef4e2dccee00151","tid":2092312,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"唔著返件 羊毛衫？"},{"pid":"c3f0ac1ea1e705a1c21a545737378a4328a69202","tid":2092312,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"個個笑得哀傷"},{"pid":"f9512d4914bf9ab6affeac610af9e30cc4dd3afe","tid":2092312,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:35:32.000Z","msg":"北半球六月落雪<br />\n六月飛霜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a58a65aaeced16820dd7fcf54666388009f32f8","tid":2092312,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"六月去新疆穿衣<br />\n<br />\n新疆6月份的平均氣溫在17到28度，北疆的溫度在28度左右，建議遊客穿襯衫、薄長裙等清涼透氣的衣服，晚上的溫度在17度左右，建議遊客穿套裝休閒裝薄毛衣等保暖的衣服。<br />\n<br />\n講緊舊年天氣"},{"pid":"d395fc4c962138027c47ae1199e0b8b6a99e496b","tid":2092312,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:01:06.000Z","msg":"下次，半個北京變鹽柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}